      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; white-space: normal;\"><div><p style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-family: &amp;apos;Helvetica Neue&amp;apos;, Helvetica, &amp;apos;Microsoft YaHei&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;apos;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(129, 124, 124); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">与PCA保持数据信息不同，LDA是为了使得降维后的数据点尽可能地容易被区分。既然是线性的，那么就是希望找到映射向量a， 使得 a‘X后的数据点能够保持以下两种性质：</p><ol style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 3em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-family: &amp;apos;Helvetica Neue&amp;apos;, Helvetica, &amp;apos;Microsoft YaHei&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;apos;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(129, 124, 124); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><li style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: decimal;\">同类数据点尽可能接近</li><li style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: decimal;\">不同类数据点尽可能分开</li></ol><p style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-family: &amp;apos;Helvetica Neue&amp;apos;, Helvetica, &amp;apos;Microsoft YaHei&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;apos;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(129, 124, 124); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">为了显示与PCA的区别，在网上找来了下面的图，PCA找到的是轴2，LDA找到的是轴1. LDA与PCA的目标不同，LDA希望降维后数据可以很容易的被分开。<br style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px;\"/><img src=\"http://www.36dsj.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/00513.jpg\" style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0.7em 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16.8px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: auto;\"/></p></div><div><br/></div><div style=\"-webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-family: &amp;apos;Helvetica Neue&amp;apos;, Helvetica, &amp;apos;Microsoft YaHei&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;apos;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(129, 124, 124); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-size: 17px;\"><div>近期也看了一篇Pacific Visualization 2016里利用LDA进行高维子空间的维度重建相关工作的论文【3】。</div><img src=\"http://i4.buimg.com/814f